    <h1 class="page-title">TodoItem</h1>
    

    




<section>

<header>
    
        <h2>
        TodoItem
        </h2>
        
            <div class="class-description"><p><code>&lt;todo-item&gt;</code> – Renders and manages a single todo entry.</p>
<p>Supports:</p>
<ul>
<li>Toggle completion</li>
<li>Inline editing (Enter/Esc)</li>
<li>Delete with confirmation</li>
<li>Visual feedback (hover, completed state, disabled edit when done)</li>
</ul></div>
        
    
</header>

<article>
    <div class="container-overview">
    
        
