<h5>Fires:</h5>
<ul>
    <li>TodoItem#event:toggle-todo   - When checkbox is changed</li>

    <li>TodoItem#event:delete-todo   - When delete button is confirmed</li>

    <li>TodoItem#event:update-todo   - When edit is saved</li>
</ul>











